  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study examines possible risk factors with regard to complications following pacemaker or
      implantable defibrillator cardioverter (ICD) implantation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study examines possible risk factors with regard to complications following pacemaker or
      implantable defibrillator cardioverter (ICD)implantation. Furthermore validation af the
      Danish Pacemaker and ICD Register will be conducted.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
